title.narrative: Empowered Citizens and Communities Demanding their Rights and Holding Duty Bearers to Account

description.narrative: Human Rights and Democratic Space: National governments and international duty-bearers adopt policies to promote democratic and transparent processes that protect and fulfil the rights of people living in poverty.

The project, aiming to empower citizens and communities will focus on achieving the following results - Women, men and youth are able to hold duty bearers to account with regards to human rights issues that affect their lives. - Human rights violations are reported and redress is attained for victims followed by evidence based advocacy. - Human rights space is held and HRDs are protected through access to legal and other services. - There is constitutional compliance and alignment of laws related to the human rights charter in the constitution. -The Consortium’s value addition is enhanced through evidence based shared knowledge and collective advocacy.
